  "texts": [
    "Table 6 presents an overview of our simulation environment.",
    "We display the comparative study of performance analysis of our protocol (named SDNwPCA) with Assistive Care Loop Framework (ACLF) and BSN-Care in terms of reliability, several error packets, and throughput.",
    "From Fig. 8, because of our lightweight proximity-based authentication and multilayer storage, our assessment of the proposed safety protocol's dependability increases over ACLF and BSN-Care (Patient Local Server, Cloud, and Blockchain).",
    "The architecture of the ACLF used a triple key feature for making lifelong activity of the sensor.",
    "Hence, if the keys are breached, then any intruder can easily get overall control of the devices."
  ]
